      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·007.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">葛藟.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>緜緜葛藟，在河之滸。終遠兄弟，謂他人父。謂他人父，亦莫我顧。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The dolichos grows luxuriant
On the branches of the jujube trees.
My brothers are all in a distant quarter,
And none of them will have me any more.
People of whom I ask, all say,
They are dead or gone away.
How can it be otherwise than that my heart should ache?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
