      <prop type="x-translation-ref">葛藟.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>緜緜葛藟，在河之漘。終遠兄弟，謂他人昆。謂他人昆，亦莫我聞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The dolichos grows luxuriant
On the branches of the sour plum trees.
My brothers are all in a distant quarter,
And none of them will attend to me.
People of whom I ask, all say,
They are dead or gone away.
How can it be otherwise than that I should sigh?</seg>
      </tuv>
